<p>
<lb n="1"/>dinakarakuluṁḍaina tribhuvanamallaṁḍu kammanāṁḍunu guṁḍikaṟṟu moṭṭavāḍiyuṁ jēkoni rūḍhigā nēlaṁgaṁ goṭṭiyadonapayanu paṭṭanamuna <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> nabhinavaraivatakādrinānoppina girimīṁdivihagēṁdrakētanunaku <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> dhanadhavaṁśēśuṁḍu penuṁgoṁḍabai 
<lb n="2" break="no"/>rapanāyaku kāpayanaṁdanuṁḍu ghanuṁḍu bayyanaseṭṭi saṁkrāṁtitithinimityamuna nētraśailaviyattalēṁdusaṁkhya sakadhāruṇipālu samamulamaraṁ brabalucuṁḍa nakhaṁḍadīpaṁbunilipe <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> 55 Ēṁbhaḍēnu velleḍlu vīni jēkoni gu
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ṁḍyabōyini koḍku nanyabōyuṁḍu tana putrānu<unclear>pau</unclear>trikamu nittya māneṁḍu neyi Akhaṇḍadīpamunaku pōyaṁgalavāṁḍu <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> svadattaṁ paradattaṁ vā yō harēti vasundharā[ṁ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g>*] ṣaṣṭirvvaruṣasahasrāṇi viṣṭāyāṁ jāyatē krimi<supplied reason="omitted">ḥ</supplied> <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
</p>

